high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the couch.
Pick up the remote off of the couch.
Turn left and walk to the chair to the right of the fireplace.
Place the remote on the front left edge of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk across the room to the black end table with a remote on it.
Pick up the remote off of the end table.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room, after that turn left and walk up to the chair to the right of the fireplace.
Put the remote on the seat of the chair to the right of the remote that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn left and go to the couch
Pick up the remote on the couch
Turn left, go to the chair
Put the remote on the chair
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward a bit, turn right, go to the drawer unit
Pick up the remote on top of the drawer unit
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the chair
Put the remote on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the chair

high_descs: Turn to the left, cross the room to the wall, hang a left and go to the couch.
Pick up the remote control that is on the couch.
Turn to the left, cross the room to the brown chair.
Put the remote control in the brown chair on the left side.
Turn to the left, go into the next room, hang a left, go forward, turn right and go to the middle black table.
Pick up the remote control that is on the black table.
Turn around, go across the room to the couch, hang a left and go to the brown chair.
Put the remote control in the brown chair to the right of the other remote control.
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls in a chair.
